ComicInfo.Summary: The plan succeeds! Gina and her allies lead the Dynasty of Stars armada into the heart of the Umbral Maliverse and strike a mortal blow...but it was too easy! Dreadwing suddenly appears to consume the falling Umbra, fusing with the demiurge's remaining power in one deft move and turning the tables on the entire galaxy! All is lost! So why is Gina grinning? This issue kicks off the eight-part finale of the Gold Digger saga. Don't miss it!
